  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter this 3D action-adventure world that will test your daring, strategy and reflexes! In this fast-paced journey, you take on the role of a fearless chicken on a mission to protect his faithful companion, Chick, from the persistent bees who are chasing him!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655200/extras/70de6d74fce0c2648900a64ae529f85f.poster.avif?t=1746611006\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655200/extras/70de6d74fce0c2648900a64ae529f85f.webm?t=1746611006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge the clock!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have 25 seconds to reach a key. Strategize and figure out how to collect all the keys before time runs out. Can you do it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Protect Chick!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your feathered friend is counting on you. Throw the shield at him when needed. Defend him from the bee attacks and keep his precious life intact. Every collision is a test of your skill – are you ready to be the hero he needs?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive visuals and sound!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although in 3D, the game features 2D explosion effects to give the player a fun cartoon feel every time a bee is blown up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655200/extras/c87b8c0bc18368e73d30d49891c65e07.poster.avif?t=1746611006\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655200/extras/c87b8c0bc18368e73d30d49891c65e07.webm?t=1746611006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655200/extras/c87b8c0bc18368e73d30d49891c65e07.mp4?t=1746611006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join the adventure now!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download <i>Chick Defender</i> and embark on a journey where every key is a step towards victory, every bee is a challenge to overcome and every round is a test of your bravery. Do you have what it takes to save Chick and show that you can reach higher and higher rounds? Prove it!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter this 3D action-adventure world that will test your daring, strategy and reflexes! In this fast-paced journey, you take on the role of a fearless chicken on a mission to protect his faithful companion, Chick, from the persistent bees who are chasing him!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655200/extras/70de6d74fce0c2648900a64ae529f85f.poster.avif?t=1746611006\" width=800 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655200/extras/70de6d74fce0c2648900a64ae529f85f.webm?t=1746611006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge the clock!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have 25 seconds to reach a key. Strategize and figure out how to collect all the keys before time runs out. Can you do it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Protect Chick!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your feathered friend is counting on you. Throw the shield at him when needed. Defend him from the bee attacks and keep his precious life intact. Every collision is a test of your skill – are you ready to be the hero he needs?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive visuals and sound!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although in 3D, the game features 2D explosion effects to give the player a fun cartoon feel every time a bee is blown up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655200/extras/c87b8c0bc18368e73d30d49891c65e07.poster.avif?t=1746611006\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655200/extras/c87b8c0bc18368e73d30d49891c65e07.webm?t=1746611006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3655200/extras/c87b8c0bc18368e73d30d49891c65e07.mp4?t=1746611006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join the adventure now!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download <i>Chick Defender</i> and embark on a journey where every key is a step towards victory, every bee is a challenge to overcome and every round is a test of your bravery. Do you have what it takes to save Chick and show that you can reach higher and higher rounds? Prove it!</p>",
